text: Wilmon is a male given name. Notable people with the name include: *Wilmon W. Blackmar (1841–1905), United States military officer *Wilmon Brewer (1895–1998), American literary scholar, poet, and philanthropist *Wilmon Newell (1878–1943), American entomologist *Wilmon Henry Sheldon (1875–1981), American philosopher ==See also== *Wilmont (disambiguation) Category:English masculine given names
title: Wilmon
